  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE QA / project gatekeeper. Verifies FR-level acceptance.</role>

  <goal>
    Documented confirmation that Phase 2 is complete: 5 new fields live; embedding extension live; drift job scheduled; admin view + button operational; validation gate working; 6 playbooks indexed; benchmark passing.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per spec.md Phase 2 acceptance + design §1.4. Exit-gate verification is a brief checklist run — no new artifacts beyond the summary doc.
