  <steps>
    <step order="1">FR-08: confirm Dataverse describe shows all 5 fields on `sprk_analysisplaybook`. Verify CDS-Solution export contains them.</step>
    <step order="2">FR-09: confirm JPS matching metadata schema doc exists; spot-validate a backfilled playbook payload.</step>
    <step order="3">FR-10: re-run benchmark from task 038 — confirm NDA query top-1.</step>
    <step order="4">FR-11: trigger "Send to Index" on a sample playbook in dev — confirm 60s status flip.</step>
    <step order="5">FR-12: send a malformed POST (missing description) — confirm 400 ProblemDetails with `MissingFields`.</step>
    <step order="6">FR-13: confirm drift job exists + scheduled. Manually trigger it; verify telemetry shows scan count.</step>
    <step order="7">FR-14: confirm "Playbook Index Drift" view appears in dev; filter logic correct.</step>
    <step order="8">Summarize results in `notes/handoffs/040-phase-2-exit.md`. Mark each FR pass/fail.</step>
    <step order="9">If all pass: update TASK-INDEX.md task 040 → ✅; Phase 2 complete. If any fail: file remediation task + flag owner.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
